                                <p>立軸</p>
                                <decoNote>
                                    A set of two hanging scrolls adorned in the two-color mount style, featuring 
                                    blue jacquard silk for the 'Heaven' section (天頭) and the 'Earth' section (地脚). 
                                    Vertical stripes (隔水) are crafted from white Chinese paper, displaying signs of 
                                    yellowing. The calligraphies are elegantly written on traditional Chinese paper 
                                    in yellow, adorned with gilt and intricate pattern decorations.
                                    立軸，裝裱方式為二色裱，天頭地脚及邊框為淺藍色有花紋絲織物,隔水為白色紙本,已汎黃。
                                    書法寫與淺棕黃色灑金絹本上,配有彩繪多寶花草紋樣邊框。上聯卷軸的天杆処有破損痕跡，
                                    略有水印污損。</decoNote>
